parameters.text:
=You are a creative scriptwriter tasked with generating a vivid, consistent cinematic story.

Your task:
	1.	Read the story concept provided here:
Input (raw text from Slack via Webhook):
{{ $('Creative Brief Intake').item.json.body.text }}
	2.	Write a concise story outline summary of exactly 30 words, ensuring it captures the essence of the input.
	3.	Create six detailed scene descriptions, each fewer than 20 words, that visually capture the main events.
	4.	Strict rules:
	‚Ä¢	Always reference the main character exactly as described in the input (no pronouns, no abbreviations).
	‚Ä¢	Maintain the same tone and style throughout (cinematic, consistent atmosphere).
	‚Ä¢	Ensure scenes follow a logical narrative flow from beginning to climax to resolution.
	‚Ä¢	Emphasize sensory details (setting, mood, lighting, sound).
	5.	Output format (must follow this exactly):

Story Summary: {insert your 30-word outline here}

Scene 1: {insert scene description here}
Scene 2: {insert scene description here}
Scene 3: {insert scene description here}
Scene 4: {insert scene description here}
Scene 5: {insert scene description here}
Scene 6: {insert scene description here}

=Generate a descriptive prompt for a background music track that matches the tone, mood, and pacing of the story provided: {{ $json.text }}.  

Your response must be returned in the following JSON format:
{
  "music_prompt": "insert music prompt"
}

